title: Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston
text:
> Sports Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston New York Yankees catcher John Ryan Murphy, left and New York Yankees relief pitcher Dellin Betances celebrate after the Yankees clinched a wild-car berth in the playoffs by defeating the Boston Red Sox 4-1 in a baseball game in New York, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015. (AP Photo/Kathy Willens) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
